# AGIB Environment Variables

## Groww Trading API (Primary market data)
```bash
# Option A: Daily access token from Groww dashboard (Trading APIs → Generate → Access Token)
GROWW_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_token_here

# Option B: API Key + Secret (checksum flow — requires daily approval)
GROWW_API_KEY=your_api_key
GROWW_API_SECRET=your_api_secret

# Optional override
GROWW_API_BASE=https://api.groww.in/v1
```

# Optional: enable Groww historical candles (3 API calls per refresh — can hit rate limits)
# GROWW_USE_HISTORICAL=true

## NewsAPI.org (server-side only — never prefix with VITE_)
# Requires a NewsAPI plan licensed for public production use.
NEWSAPI_KEY=your_newsapi_key_here

## Nifty 500 public research (server/worker only — never prefix with VITE_)
# Supabase project URL and a service-role key used only by the backend and
# scheduled Python research worker. Do not expose this key to the browser.
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_server_only_service_role_key

# Comma-separated IST schedule for the Nifty 500 research worker.
# Default: 16:15 (after market close). Optional: 08:30,12:30,16:15
NIFTY500_SCHEDULE_TIMES_IST=16:15
NIFTY500_CONSTITUENTS_PATH=./Nifty500.csv
# Do not replace the current public dataset with a materially incomplete run.
NIFTY500_MINIMUM_PUBLISH_COVERAGE=0.95

## Existing variables
See server/index.js and src/lib/supabaseClient.js for INDIANAPI_KEY, PERPLEXITY_KEY, SUPABASE_*, etc.
